description: Redevelopment of the site incorporating the erection of a part 4/ part 5 storey building fronting York Road, and a 3-5 storey building partially fronting Chatfield Road and extending to part 5/ part 6 storey building to the rear to provide a total of 51 residential units (including balconies and terraces), 362 sqm of retail space (use class A1), 155 sqm of office space (use class B1a); excavation of basement to provide a car park (accessed off Chatfield Road), ancillary works and landscaping.
